headline: PRGS Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Rise Y/Y, Shares Up
summary: Progress Software tops Q4 earnings estimates as revenue jumps 18% year over year, ARR grows, and upbeat fiscal 2026 guidance sends shares up nearly 9% in pre-market.
